alternate.name: Links to an alternate version of the document (i.e. print page, translated or mirror)

external.name: Resource is linked outside the current domain

author.name: Links to the author of the document

license.name: Links to copyright information for the document

next.name: The next document in a selection

nofollow.name: Links to an unendorsed document, like a paid link.

noreferrer.name: Specifies that the browser should not send a HTTP referer header if the user follows the hyperlink

prefetch.name: Specifies that the target document should be cached

prev.name: The previous document in a selection

search.name: Links to a search tool for the document

tag.name: A tag (keyword) for the current document
